{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 81064, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "A-其实还好拿吧？", "timestamp": 1593824943, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81066, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "旧绩点很多专业课均分是绝对不到3.0的，大一微积分线代平均分好像是C-（问过助教）", "timestamp": 1593824945, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81069, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: C-是1.7吧？", "timestamp": 1593824999, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81080, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 我大一上微积分C，问助教助教说不错了总评平均是C-，佛了", "timestamp": 1593825179, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81677, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz你真的经历过旧绩点吗。。水B+？旧绩点都是卷A/A+的好吗", "timestamp": 1593832966, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81854, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 对呀，人的精力是有限的啊，重要的课卷到A/A+就好，其他课水水到B+就好\n毕竟我们比不了全卷A的大佬", "timestamp": 1593835714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81875, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那也没人逼你全卷到A-以上啊?这和绩点有关系吗", "timestamp": 1593836029, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81893, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 改革不改革 卷王都是一样卷。如果对你来说，你觉得现在都要卷到A-以上，那以前就是全要卷到A以上，所以无法理解你所说观点", "timestamp": 1593836149, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81899, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 13957, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 你可以这么理解，旧绩点下一种人要所有课（包括很多没用的课）全都卷到A-，一种人把重要的课卷到A，其他课随便水水拿个B或者B+，旧绩点下两种人绩点可能差不多，而新绩点通货膨胀，第一种人比第二种人绩点高的多，就是逼着所有人用第一种卷法", "timestamp": 1593836482, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 13957, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "感觉新绩点比旧绩点卷多了...... \n旧绩点只需要选喜欢，重要的几门课卷到A，剩下的课水到B+左右就行；新绩点所有课都要卷到A-以上；\n感觉这样学到的有用的东西越来越少了（虽然你清课程有用的东西比例也不大）", "timestamp": 1593824857, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782588, "url": "", "vote": {}}}